data.description: ***FRESHLY PAINTED, PROFESSIONALLY CLEANED, AND MOVE IN READY*** Welcome home to the highly coveted Carolina Plantations neighborhood. This single story 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home is the perfect place to create memories and live a life of convenience. Located close to the best shopping Jacksonville has to offer, you'll love the ease of access to shopping and entertainment and will find that the proximity to the bypass makes an easy commute to work where-ever you are headed. The large kitchen island is the highlight of the home providing a fantastic area for meal prep or entertaining while the open concept space allows you to continue to be a part of the every day or part of the party. The 2 car garage offers plenty of parking and storage space while the covered back porch and fully fenced yard ensures all your needs are met. Call today for your personal tour!
